headline.main: Syrian Pilot Whose Plane Crashed in Turkey Says Aircraft Shot Down en Route to Idlib
headline.print_headline: Syrian Pilot Whose Plane Crashed in Turkey Says Aircraft Shot Down en Route to Idlib

lead_paragraph: A Syrian air force pilot who bailed out as his warplane crashed on Turkish territory told a Turkish rescue team his MiG-23 had been shot down, Turkey's state-run Anadolu news agency reported on Sunday.
